EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
DNC 19.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS IN PROGRESS UNTIL 161900Z SEP
   WITHIN 30 MILES OF 57-27.6N 008-23.1W.

   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 OR

2. CANCEL THIS MSG 162000Z SEP 15.
